\begin_layout Standard
“基本无振荡 (essentially non-oscillatory, ENO)” 方法始于 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "Harten--Engquist--Osher--Chakravarthy (1987)"
target "https://doi.org/10.1016/0021-9991(87)90031-3"
literal "false"

